    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In eterni Dei omnipotentis nomine amen. Brevis causa memorie descriptus,
                        qualiter factum est apud <placeName ref="#places/63"
                            key="#Baptismal_churches">Sanctam Mariam ad Montem</placeName> et in
                            <orgName key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/72"><rs
                                key="#Baptismal_churches">plebe</rs> eius loci</orgName>, et
                        presentia <rs key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">bonorum hominum</rs> quorum
                        nomina subter scripta reperiuntur. <persName ref="#people/3217"
                            >Adimarius</persName> quondam <persName ref="#people/3218"
                            >Alberti</persName> et <persName><name ref="Sardus"
                            >Sardus</name></persName> filius eius (…) liberaverunt et remiserunt
                            <persName key="#Judge"><name ref="Rodelandus">Rolando</name>
                            <rs key="#Judge">iudici</rs></persName> ad opus <orgName
                            key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals"
                                >hospitalis</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207"
                            >Altepascensis</placeName></orgName> illam terre petiam et ius tenienti
                        ex ea eis pertinentibus que est posita in loco et finibus <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210" key="#Rivers">Putei</placeName> et iusta <rs
                            key="#Rivers">aquam Iussianam</rs> quam <persName><name ref="Nerus"
                                >Nerus</name></persName> quondam *** eis iudicavit vel donavit et
                        ius et proprietas est suprascripti hospitalis. Et ipsam terram dictus Nerus
                        ab ipso hospitali detinebat. Que vero tenet ambo capita cum uno latere in
                        terra suprascripti hospitalis, latus aliud tenet in terra eiusdem Adimarii
                        et Sardi. (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: dupli dicte rei. <rs
                            key="#Meritum/launechild"><foreign>Meritum</foreign>: quadraginta sol.
                            bonorum denariorum pisane monete</rs>. (…) Quod actum est anno
                        nativitate Christi millesimo centesimo nonagesimo primo, tertio idus madii,
                        indictione nona. Et presentia <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Iacobus"
                            >Iacopi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Widaloctus"
                                >Guidalotti</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Robertus"
                                >Roberti</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Robertus"
                                >Robertini</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Armanectus"
                                >Armannetti</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Iordanus"
                                >Iordanis</name></persName> rogatorum <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testium</rs>. (S) Ego <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Leonardus">Leonardus</name></persName> doni imperatoris <rs
                            key="#Notary">notarius</rs> predictis interfui, ideoque hec causa
                        memorie <rs key="#Writer">in his publicis scriptis redegi</rs> et dedi.</ab>
